---
title: Apricot Haloumi & Mumbai Veggie Toss with Garlic Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful paneer
coated in apricot sauce meets roasted vegetables tossed with Mumbai-style spices, and there’s a tangy
yoghurt dressing to finish it off.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
